data.description: 3bd-2bth home in Northwest Dallas backs directly to desirable NORTHAVEN TRAIL greenbelt!!! Inviting neighborhood with nearby community pool club, Royal Park sport courts & playground. Over 2000 sqft on nearly a quarter-acre lot means plenty of inside-outdoor space...with several flexible living areas and large back yard enclosed by stained wood privacy fence. Ensuite primary; Secondary bedrooms share full bath. Sunlit kitchen features stainless steel gas range, island with counter seating, and sleek concrete floors. Beautiful built-ins by the bright bay window create a lovely focal point. Garage converted into ample den with extra closet storage + pantry & utility room. Less than a mile from Degolyer Elementary and Park Forest Branch Library. Convenient access to I-635 & I-35E makes for a quick commute in any direction.
